    <statement><div><p>Simplify the expression below:</p>

<p><me>
{8}{b}^0
</me></p>

<p><fillin characters="15" name="ans1"/>  </p></div></statement>
    <solution><div><h3>Worked Solution</h3>

<p>The zero index law states that any non-zero quantity raised to the power zero equals 1.</p>

<p><me>
{b}^0 = 1.
</me></p>

<p>So the expression becomes:</p>

<p><me>
{8} \times 1 = {8}.
</me></p></div></solution>
    <answer><p><m>8</m></p></answer>
